{"tid":1370214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出發前！727元朗手足溫馨提示","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:45:49.000Z","uid":265443,"like":484,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"2e36f4a3faca9023c51a8b30a7fc45e01c91d0d0","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"純copy and paste, 覺得有用與否請自行判斷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qknqLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qknqLB.png&h=8901d6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n727 的元朗手足，以下是我溫馨提示（根據我的情報）<br />\n<br />\n1. 大馬路、安寧路及教育路<br />\n- 阿婆阿伯會潑屎尿<br />\n- 唐樓藍絲/建制派會高空擲物<br />\n<br />\n🎈頭盔、雨傘☂️<br />\n🎈多一、兩件衫<br />\n🎈環保袋<br />\n<br />\n❌不上唐樓及唐樓天台（有被圍捕，包抄風險）<br />\n✅單憧樓有lift 有保安相對安全<br />\n<br />\n2、兩個西鐵站<br />\n- 會有便衣、鄕黑哨兵及文大商（中共媒體）<br />\n<br />\n🎈盡量帶口罩<br />\n<br />\n3 南邊圍（擴大至五圍＋山貝）+大旗嶺以下<br />\n- 鄉黑駐重兵及「農具」<br />\n<br />\n❌不入村<br />\n🛎一齊入一齊走 （對準政權：中聯辦及中共走狗）<br />\n🛑一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n📍其他<br />\n&middot;足夠水足夠乾糧<br />\n&middot;帶毛巾<br />\n&middot;避入教會（宣道會元基堂，康樂路嘉好樓二樓）（安寧路基督教香港信義會生命堂）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⭕️yoho 、朗八、晴朗及橫洲的友好居民及村民，若有突變，上番樓，留在家。"},{"pid":"6eafa04d19b7318af9a340d523c37d7d62c01d94","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b22b49d681d367c95e925af076f0b187f3032aa","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbdb33f624a07e6fa915abdf94478d9712c631df","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d065d9c6a473260189800640f52dfde59fddef7","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56ab5026526515af9280945f15770dfb01e066e8","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:29:37.000