ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老強做處長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有反送中嘅我哋被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄉黑勢力擴大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警濫權繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治形同虛設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土共全面接管香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會再咁易反抗到港共、土共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反送中傳媒被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706888b1eb494e7fec3735596ce617ce01f6d2f6","tid":1370214,"uid":236183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"帶memo 紙"},{"pid":"faaa223502f5fc2b68d7543aa6791b0455752c4c","tid":1370214,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"去完元朗旅行買老婆餅 可以出返中聯辦路祭李鵬<br />\n之後又去金鐘野下餐 睇下班狗跟得去邊"},{"pid":"1e2186ecfb138b50264746a5798d5ec9350f174e","tid":1370214,"uid":205552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85e81361a6273b533612cac0894588303a7b648f","tid":1370214,"uid":57328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqOzi.png&h=002dc61c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n更新左加入更多地標, 遊行路線, 有意見隨時回答, 謝"},{"pid":"31c3abfae82b44e2c329ea54ea7ff205b89ca563","tid":1370214,"uid":263618,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"一定唔可以入村<br />\n一定唔可以入村<br />\n一定唔可以入村<br />\n<br />\n重要嘅嘢要講三次"},{"pid":"9c1ad0c2542443416018867907127960b02d8312","tid":1370214,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2826bb6a9804f200cd36af3a35c8c6379c083d64","tid":1370214,"uid":95393,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好入村唔好搞祠堂</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好入村唔好搞祠堂</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好入村唔好搞祠堂</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好入村唔好搞祠堂</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好入村唔好搞祠堂</span><br />\n<br />\n成場運動越走越多人加入<br />\n難得有少少希望<br />\n大家忍耐少少唔好中計<br />\n當一搞到市民資產係好難翻案, 呢個係林鄭最想<br />\n如果你見到手足想衝入村<br />\n麻煩你捉住佢俾佢冷靜下"},{"pid":"170830b297465a6b5696dd3109c26e94f5f87139","tid":1370214,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bd4706b6b603fdaf32d0e6552a2f6177da4d2d","tid":1370214,"uid":257593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬事小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be195e62360e454a11827dec19b3bbc728aab15","tid":1370214,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45f6e00deaae0238d7fb46652950eb9e3c0b0f7d","tid":1370214,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:49:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6ebafc0f5e61ba265b90d42fd429f65dfe771b02","tid":1370214,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:49:57.000Z","msg":"其實而家係水邊定元西集合"},{"pid":"685684bbd4cd47d0ac6c17181f0908934262d335","tid":1370214,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e36f4a3faca9023c51a8b30a7fc45e01c91d0d0","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:28:29