ormal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阻止到老強做處長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土共冇咁易控制香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同何妖做清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同cctvb紅媒做清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輸咗：進入黑暗時代<br />\n全港監控鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老強做處長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有反送中嘅我哋被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄉黑勢力擴大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警濫權繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治形同虛設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土共全面接管香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會再咁易反抗到港共、土共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反送中傳媒被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"要贏今日就千祈唔好畀人引咗入村,小心!"},{"pid":"4ac5a2550c3469a79a4f55ed2c40abb26373622b","tid":1370214,"uid":250023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa9e9cf176daf0420216aef7aba9f9b13b8df199","tid":1370214,"uid":19209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1102c33f290536e6cd48bff8ef08f6d4e9d24ce","tid":1370214,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46226c79c5691e0e849f56f206fe8d6d56653b4d","tid":1370214,"uid":26338