s/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同何妖做清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同cctvb紅媒做清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輸咗：進入黑暗時代<br />\n全港監控鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老強做處長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有反送中嘅我哋被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄉黑勢力擴大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警濫權繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治形同虛設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土共全面接管香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會再咁易反抗到港共、土共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反送中傳媒被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"要贏今日就千祈唔好畀人引咗入村,小心!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:18:02.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"109a335f2a17f89a7738d448035f435888b4c25a","tid":1370214,"uid":235458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"其實大家係幾點邊到開始 完全搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1078db5566760389f540404424e904a270284162","tid":1370214,"uid":211993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9841cad63ae2a53e0fb268c672764e279932be03","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109a335f2a17f89a7738d448035f435888b4c25a","tid":1370214,"uid":235458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"其實大家係幾點邊到開始 完全搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"我自己大約1點到，唔係遊行，無特定時間"},{"pid":"a4aa1814b462c69424b423f7b56b60812661450d","tid":1370214,"uid":154812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:19:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d2dcf21eef81f9378896386dfb805460f222831e","tid":1370214,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc80f84e3ac629683a6e17b08ba061409e75c816","tid":1370214,"uid":235458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9841cad63ae2a53e0fb268c672764e279932be03","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109a335f2a17f89a7738d448035f435888b4c25a","tid":1370214,"uid":235458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"其實大家係幾點邊到開始 完全搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"我自己大約1點到，唔係遊行，無特定時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"明白 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e83aa606cbcda9457e798308e85dc94004f4948","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"578e40ef3122d3259ec5beeac348771f6afe1b91","tid":1370214,"uid":117084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"727"},{"pid":"ed0eb8671de5edf3877b5047960f53aa213bc2d0","tid":1370214,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e36f4a3faca9023c51a8b30a7fc45e01c91d0d0","tid":1370214,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"純copy and paste, 覺得有用與否請自行判斷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qknqLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qknqLB.png&h=8901d6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n727 的元朗手足，以下是我溫馨提示（根據我的情報）<br />\n<br />\n1. 大馬路、安寧路及教育路<br />\n- 阿婆阿伯會潑屎尿<br />\n- 唐樓藍絲/建制派會高空擲物<br />\n<br />\n🎈頭盔、雨傘☂️<br />\n🎈多一、兩件衫<br />\n🎈環保袋<br />\n<br />\n❌不上唐樓及唐樓天台（有被圍捕，包抄風險）<br />\n✅單憧樓有lift 有保安相對安全<br />\n<br />\n2、兩個西鐵站<br />\n- 會有便衣、鄕黑哨兵及文大商（中共媒體）<br />\n<br />\n🎈盡量帶口罩<br />\n<br />\n3 南邊圍（擴大至五圍＋山貝）+大旗嶺以下<br />\n- 鄉黑駐重兵及「農具」<br />\n<br />\n❌不入村<br />\n🛎一齊入一齊走 （對準政權：中聯辦及中共走狗）<br />\n🛑一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n📍其他<br />\n&middot;足夠水足夠乾糧<br />\n&middot;帶毛巾<br />\n&middot;避入教會（宣道會元基堂，康樂路嘉好樓二樓）（安寧路基督教香港信義會生命堂）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⭕️yoho 、朗八、晴朗及橫洲的友好居民及村民，若有突變，上番樓，留在家。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"有咩事又屈你集體打交<br />\n聚集就話你非法遊行<br />\n<br />\n大家都眼見近日元朗新聞<br />\n咁都可以指麇為那 癲倒是非<br />\n<br />\n大家自問一下，<br />\n做下心理功課，諗下應對，<br />\n以免入村變入侵，又有人保家衛國。<br />\n人太多就話非集<br />\n<br />\n1. 有人沖入，你跟唔跟<br />\n2. 村入面有人撩你，你沖唔沖<br />\n3. 有人打完手足，龜入村，你沖唔沖<br />\n4. 有人捉左手足入村，救唔救！<br />\n5. 警察三面圍迫，焗你入村<br />\n6. 圍村要交人，圍幾耐，點進行下一步<br />\n7. 如果非法遊行被捉，點做？<br />\n8. 今日瘋狂捉人身份證，<br />\n然後對比電訊商資料點應對，點自辯黎全身裝黎食野。<br />\n<br />\n一定要記者<br />\n拍片紀錄係最強大武器<br />\n<br />\n一定要先禮後兵<br />\n有聲公講清楚發生咩事，唔要得口號。<br />\n就算手捉被人捉左入村！"},{"pid":"1773285f047368dd5fdc4c96b6cb70df9817b40d","tid":1370214,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037fdc3a99a3e43897b3e41c6a8788c17573564d","tid":1370214,"uid":268824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2596c34649a7e790c58ace75fcacf5e8a1703507","tid":1370214,"uid":239510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"推返上去 出面好多廢po<br />\n<br />\n過期野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4978522e1698f5595ea9942d19fe9e71cf33b2","tid":1370214,"uid":23954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"Yoho 2期（西鐵站）停車場走到最上係私人住宅平台"},{"pid":"21092f8a93ae58119512b92e6bdc78bac10efd98","tid":1370214,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-